author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! Moderation can be hit or miss when it comes to the Internet, but in the case of "Slope's Game Room" it's certainly missed the mark, his channel is facing a deletion on YouTube for something he did in a totally different service on Google. Why? Let's find out! Thanks for watching!

title: Don’t Delete This Channel Google…
